  "description": "<i>Phineas and Ferb: Quest for Cool Stuff</i> is a 3D action-adventure game based on the <i> Phineas and Ferb </i> Disney XD cartoon series. In the last week of the summer vacation Phineas and Ferb decide to open up a museum and are off to find cool stuff to exhibit. <br><br>In this single player side scrolling platformer you play as Perry, Phineas and Ferb and have to collect all kinds of stuff. First you have to build a walking robot that Phineas and Ferb can operate. The robot has tools to drill through walls and can be used as a submarine. Along the way enemies have to be defeated and your robots paintjob is customizable.",
